properties.sql:
/*Diligências Filtro Hipotecas*/
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, null AS outorgaIniciada, null AS EstadoConclusoes, sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, dp.c_urgencia AS Urgencia, null AS PID, null as OrigemProcesso, dp.c_nome_banco AS NomeBanco, dp.c_n_wf_banco AS NumeroWFBanco, dp.c_n_wf_pl as NumeroWFPL, dp.c_tipo_processo as TipoProcesso, dp.c_nome_cliente as NomeCliente, c_estado_contratacao AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, null as DataInicio, null as DataFim, ip.c_nome AS Cliente, null AS DataAgendamento, null AS AnoAgendamento, null AS MesAgendamento, null as entidadeAutenticadora, null as SLADuracao, interp.c_intervencao_juridica, interp.c_intervencao_juridica_novo, p.c_servico as Servico, null as DateModified, null as inicializacaoGestor, null as CategoriaProcesso, null as UrgenciaRegisto, null as EstadoAgendamento, null as DataAgendamentoFiltro, null as AtoStatus, null as DepositoPago, null as RegistoPago, null as Pendencia, null AS estadoArquivo
FROM shkprocesses sp 
JOIN app_fd_info_diligencia d on sp.Id = d.c_id_diligencia
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id 
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State 
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_processos_hip p ON p.id = d.c_id_processo 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_proce_hip dp ON dp.id = p.c_detalhe_processo
LEFT JOIN app_fd_interv_processo interp ON interp.c_id_processo = p.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_interv_processo_hip ip ON ip.c_id_processo = p.id AND ip.c_cliente_principal = 'CHECK' 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_agendamento_hip ag ON ag.id = p.c_agendamento
WHERE sps.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running' AND (ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.not_running.not_started' OR ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running') 
AND sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%'
AND d.id LIKE '%hipotecas%'
AND d.c_diligencia_prioritaria = 0)

/*Diligências Geral*/
UNION
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, null AS outorgaIniciada, null AS EstadoConclusoes, sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, dp.c_urgencia AS Urgencia, dp.c_pid AS PID, dp.c_origem_processo as OrigemProcesso, dp.c_nome_banco AS NomeBanco, dp.c_n_wf_banco AS NumeroWFBanco, dp.c_n_wf_pl as NumeroWFPL, dp.c_tipo_processo as TipoProcesso, dp.c_nome_cliente as NomeCliente, c_estado_contratacao AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, p.dateCreated as DataInicio,sla.c_data_fim as DataFim, ip.c_nome AS Cliente, CONCAT(ato.c_dataOutorga, ' ', ato.c_horaOutorga) AS DataAgendamento, SUBSTRING_INDEX(ato.c_dataOutorga, '-', -1) AS AnoAgendamento, SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(ato.c_dataOutorga, '-', 2), '-', -1) AS MesAgendamento, null as entidadeAutenticadora, sla.c_duracao as SLADuracao, interp.c_intervencao_juridica, interp.c_intervencao_juridica_novo, p.c_servico as Servico, null as DateModified, dp.c_inicializacao_gestor as inicializacaoGestor, null as CategoriaProcesso, null as UrgenciaRegisto, null as EstadoAgendamento, ato.c_dataOutorga as DataAgendamentoFiltro, null as AtoStatus,null as DepositoPago, null as RegistoPago, null as Pendencia, null AS estadoArquivo
FROM shkprocesses sp 
JOIN app_fd_info_diligencia d ON sp.Id = d.id 
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State 
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id 
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State 
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_processos p ON p.id = d.c_id_processo 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_processo dp ON dp.id = p.c_detalhe_processo 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_interv_processo interp ON interp.c_id_processo = p.id 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_sla_atividade sla ON sla.c_id_processo = sp.Id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_intervenientes_proc ip ON ip.c_id_processo = p.id AND ip.c_cliente_principal = 'CHECK' 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_agendamento ag ON ag.id = p.c_agendamento
LEFT JOIN app_fd_atos ato ON ato.c_id_agendamento = ag.id AND (ato.c_status = 'AGD' OR ato.c_status = 'OUT')
WHERE sps.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running' AND (ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.not_running.not_started' OR ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running') 
AND (sla.c_estado_atividade is null or sla.c_estado_atividade = 'Em curso' or sla.c_estado_atividade = 'Pendente') 
AND sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%'
AND d.c_diligencia_prioritaria = 0)


/*Processos CH*/
UNION
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, doc.c_outorga_iniciada AS outorgaIniciada, g.c_estadosConclusoes AS EstadoConclusoes, sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, dp.c_urgencia AS Urgencia, dp.c_pid AS PID, dp.c_origem_processo as OrigemProcesso, dp.c_nome_banco AS NomeBanco, dp.c_n_wf_banco AS NumeroWFBanco, dp.c_n_wf_pl as NumeroWFPL, dp.c_tipo_processo as TipoProcesso, dp.c_nome_cliente as NomeCliente, c_estado_contratacao AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, sla.c_data_inicio as DataInicio, sla.c_data_fim as DataFim, ip.c_nome AS Cliente, IF(ato.c_status = 'AGD' OR ato.c_status = 'OUT' OR ato.c_status = 'ACOM' OR ato.c_status = 'NOUT', CONCAT(ato.c_dataOutorga, ' ', ato.c_horaOutorga),'-') AS DataAgendamento, SUBSTRING_INDEX(ato.c_dataOutorga, '-', -1) AS AnoAgendamento, SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(ato.c_dataOutorga, '-', 2), '-', -1) AS MesAgendamento, ato.c_cedula_entidade as entidadeAutenticadora, sla.c_duracao as SLADuracao, interp.c_intervencao_juridica, interp.c_intervencao_juridica_novo, p.c_servico as Servico, dp.dateModified as DateModified, dp.c_inicializacao_gestor as inicializacaoGestor, dp.c_categoria_processo as CategoriaProcesso, dp.c_urgencia_registo as UrgenciaRegisto,  ato.c_status as EstadoAgendamento, ato.c_dataOutorga as DataAgendamentoFiltro, ato.c_status as AtoStatus,doc.c_deposito_pago as DepositoPago, doc.c_registo_pago as RegistoPago, doc.c_inserida_pendencia as Pendencia, g.c_estado_arquivo AS estadoArquivo
FROM shkprocesses sp
JOIN app_fd_processos p ON sp.ActivityRequesterProcessId = p.id 
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State 
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id 
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State 
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_processo dp ON dp.id = p.c_detalhe_processo 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_interv_processo interp ON interp.c_id_processo = p.id 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_sla_atividade sla ON sla.c_id_processo = sp.Id 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_intervenientes_proc ip ON ip.c_id_processo = p.id AND ip.c_cliente_principal = 'CHECK' 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_agendamento ag ON ag.id = p.c_agendamento 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_docs_processo doc ON doc.id = p.c_docs
LEFT JOIN app_fd_atos ato ON ato.c_id_agendamento = ag.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_geral g ON g.c_id_processo = p.id
WHERE sps.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running' AND (ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.not_running.not_started' OR ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running') 
AND (c_estado_contratacao is null or (c_estado_contratacao <> 'PND' AND c_estado_contratacao <> 'PNDEQ')) 
AND (sla.c_estado_atividade is null or sla.c_estado_atividade = 'Em curso' or sla.c_estado_atividade = 'Pendente') 
AND sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%'
AND (ato.dateCreated = (SELECT MAX(dateCreated) FROM app_fd_atos a2 WHERE a2.c_id_processo = p.id) || ato.dateCreated IS null)
ORDER BY Urgencia DESC, DataFim)

/*Procuradoria*/
UNION
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, null AS outorgaIniciada, null AS EstadoConclusoes, sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, null AS Urgencia, null AS PID, null as OrigemProcesso, dp.c_banco_fundo AS NomeBanco, dp.c_n_processo AS NumeroWFBanco, dp.c_n_agenda as NumeroWFPL, dp.c_tipo_processo as TipoProcesso, null as NomeCliente, dp.c_estado AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, sla.c_data_inicio as DataInicio, sla.c_data_fim as DataFim, null AS Cliente, IF(ato.c_status = 'AGD' OR ato.c_status = 'OUT' OR ato.c_status = 'ACOM' OR ato.c_status = 'NOUT', CONCAT(ato.c_dataOutorga, ' ', ato.c_horaOutorga),'-') AS DataAgendamento, SUBSTRING_INDEX(ato.c_dataOutorga, '-', -1) AS AnoAgendamento, SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(ato.c_dataOutorga, '-', 2), '-', -1) AS MesAgendamento, null as entidadeAutenticadora, sla.c_duracao as SLADuracao, null, null, p.c_servico as Servico, null as DateModified, null as inicializacaoGestor, null as CategoriaProcesso, null as UrgenciaRegisto, null as EstadoAgendamento, null as DataAgendamentoFiltro, ato.c_status as AtoStatus, null as DepositoPago, null as RegistoPago, null as Pendencia, null AS estadoArquivo
FROM shkprocesses sp
JOIN app_fd_processos_procu p ON sp.ActivityRequesterProcessId = p.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_proce_procu dp ON p.c_detalhe_processo = dp.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_sla_atividade sla ON sla.c_id_processo = sp.Id AND (c_estado_atividade = 'Em curso')
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId
LEFT JOIN app_fd_atos ato ON ato.c_id_processo = p.id 
WHERE sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%'
AND (ato.dateCreated = (SELECT MAX(dateCreated) FROM app_fd_atos a2 WHERE a2.c_id_processo = p.id) || ato.dateCreated IS null)
ORDER BY Urgencia DESC, DataFim)

/*Distrates*/
UNION
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, null AS outorgaIniciada, null AS EstadoConclusoes, sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, null AS Urgencia, null AS PID, null as OrigemProcesso, null AS NomeBanco, dp.c_num_pedido AS NumeroWFBanco, null as NumeroWFPL, dp.c_tipo_distrate as TipoProcesso, null as NomeCliente, dp.c_estado_distrate AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, null as DataInicio, null as DataFim, null AS Cliente, null AS DataAgendamento, null AS AnoAgendamento, null AS MesAgendamento, null as entidadeAutenticadora, null as SLADuracao, null, null, p.c_servico as Servico, null as DateModified, null as inicializacaoGestor, null as CategoriaProcesso, null as UrgenciaRegisto, null as EstadoAgendamento, null as DataAgendamentoFiltro,null as AtoStatus, null as DepositoPago, null as RegistoPago, null as Pendencia, null AS estadoArquivo
FROM shkprocesses sp
JOIN app_fd_processos_distrates p ON sp.ActivityRequesterProcessId = p.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_proce_dist dp ON p.c_detalhe_processo = dp.id
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId
WHERE sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%'
ORDER BY Urgencia DESC, DataFim)

/*Hipotecas*/
UNION
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, null AS outorgaIniciada, null AS EstadoConclusoes, sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, dp.c_urgencia AS Urgencia, null AS PID, null as OrigemProcesso, dp.c_nome_banco AS NomeBanco, dp.c_n_wf_banco AS NumeroWFBanco, dp.c_n_wf_pl as NumeroWFPL, dp.c_tipo_processo_final as TipoProcesso, dp.c_nome_cliente as NomeCliente, dp.c_estado_contratacao AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, null as DataInicio, null as DataFim, ip.c_nome AS Cliente, null AS DataAgendamento, null AS AnoAgendamento, null AS MesAgendamento, null as entidadeAutenticadora, null as SLADuracao, null, null, p.c_servico as Servico, null as DateModified, null as inicializacaoGestor, null as CategoriaProcesso, null as UrgenciaRegisto, null as EstadoAgendamento, null as DataAgendamentoFiltro,null as AtoStatus, null as DepositoPago, null as RegistoPago, null as Pendencia, null AS estadoArquivo
FROM shkprocesses sp
JOIN app_fd_processos_hip p ON sp.ActivityRequesterProcessId = p.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_proce_hip dp ON p.c_detalhe_processo = dp.id
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_interv_processo_hip ip ON ip.c_id_processo = p.id AND ip.c_cliente_principal = 'CHECK' 
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId
WHERE sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%'
ORDER BY Urgencia DESC, DataFim)

/*Crédito Pessoal*/
UNION
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, null AS outorgaIniciada, null AS EstadoConclusoes, 
		sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, null AS Urgencia, null AS PID, null as OrigemProcesso, null AS NomeBanco, null AS NumeroWFBanco, 
        null as NumeroWFPL, null as TipoProcesso, null as NomeCliente, null AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, 
        from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, null as DataInicio, null as DataFim, null AS Cliente, null AS DataAgendamento, null AS AnoAgendamento, 
        null AS MesAgendamento, null as entidadeAutenticadora, null as SLADuracao, null, null, p.c_servico as Servico, null as DateModified, null as inicializacaoGestor, 
        null as CategoriaProcesso, null as UrgenciaRegisto, null as EstadoAgendamento, null as DataAgendamentoFiltro,null as AtoStatus, null as DepositoPago, null as RegistoPago, 
        null as Pendencia, null AS estadoArquivo
FROM shkprocesses sp
JOIN app_fd_processos_cp p ON sp.Id = p.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_proce_cp dp ON p.c_detalhe_processo = dp.id
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId
WHERE sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%')

/*Habilitação Herdeiros*/
UNION
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, null AS outorgaIniciada, null AS EstadoConclusoes, 
		sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, null AS Urgencia, null AS PID, null as OrigemProcesso, null AS NomeBanco, null AS NumeroWFBanco, 
        dp.c_numero_processo as NumeroWFPL, dp.c_faseProcesso as TipoProcesso, null as NomeCliente, null AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, 
        from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, null as DataInicio, null as DataFim, null AS Cliente, null AS DataAgendamento, null AS AnoAgendamento, 
        null AS MesAgendamento, null as entidadeAutenticadora, null as SLADuracao, null, null, p.c_servico as Servico, dp.c_data_entrada as DateModified, null as inicializacaoGestor, 
        null as CategoriaProcesso, null as UrgenciaRegisto, null as EstadoAgendamento, null as DataAgendamentoFiltro,null as AtoStatus, null as DepositoPago, null as RegistoPago, 
        null as Pendencia, null AS estadoArquivo
FROM shkprocesses sp
JOIN app_fd_processos_hh p ON sp.Id = p.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_proce_hh dp ON p.c_detalhe_processo = dp.id
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId
WHERE sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%')
